snippet.textDisplay: Rap hai sara Rap Rap Rap hai sara Rap -x4, Rap e Flow Tez Baya’n Degey Baya’n Slow Maza Kana Wahdy Daranthy Koloh Fast Baya’n Chesth Baya’n Doroh Bly Yakk’e Line’a Mager Maro Zeyada Burz Na Jaal Boro Don’t go up or down Yo! Ni Bana Wsh Tayi Rap e Flow Ni Kana Wsh Tayi Rap Glow Chush Maza Kana Tayi Sajjey Show Pada Banay Tao MC Pro, Rap’e Andaaz Ishiye Toka Nesth Hech Raaz Flow Beka Tao Beat’o’Saaz Gura Bani Wath Sak Wsh Baaz Anchu Rail pa Rail Jhaaz Pa Jhaaz Aaap Pa Aaap, Aaas Pa Aaas, Haqiqath Pa Rapper Fouji Pa Mahaaz, Zuban Pa Arabi Shayar Pa Faraz, Rap’e Shayari Anchu Beba’n Ky Lekketha Wathi Life’e Sara Diary Zaher Beba’n Tayi Sajjey Galathi o Maheeri Kessah Cherain o Zaaheri Lafz Jaduwi o Saahiri Zubaan Degey ya Maadari, Rap’e’Sarhaal Methagi Jawar’o Gaal Chu Raway Burza Chu Raway Jaal Sarpad Beka Chu Chu’n Bani Sawaal Che Tayi Sonch’e Che Hasthy Khayal Kaye Tayi Dushmin’e Kaye Hasthy Mayaar Kaye Tayi Dost’e Kaye Tayi Yaar Kaye Ganok’e Kaye Hasthy Saar Kuja Rooch’e Kuja Kuja Hasthy Tahar Kaye Tara Looti Kaye Warthy Zaar Rap hai saara Rap Rap Rap hai saara Rap -x3. Koppi Sharab’an Kan Kasha Man Kana Beya Beka Nasha Jiye Shah, Bogo Shah, Rap Shah Ni Flow’a Tao Wath Bechar Kappy Lafz’a Lekk Ketaab’a Tahari’a Nend Rok Kaa’n Chirag’a Angha Wsh Lekky, Shoro Bebaye Soraga Naye Mushkil Khali Door Beka Ghansag’a Anchu Bandik Pa Suchen, Suchen Pa Moraga Morag Chu’n Dooch’a Wsh Laggi Pooshak’a Rap Anchu Washy, Eh Mani Goshag’a Gushag Gushag’a Zalim’a Took Koshish Bebaye Wsh Goshook Naam’a Bil Beka Sonch’a Rok Lekk Sekk Daa’n Maany Sookh Lekkag’a Nend Nibb’a Prosh Maany Soddh Tara Maany Hosh Na na bity socha bagosh Ilm’e Kadd’a Konch Baloch, Burza Flow’e Zikr Ko Tayi Gosh’a Sho Ya Wath Ma Borth Bogo Haqq’a Chu Ma Zorth Kaya Jath Rap Man Ya Tao, Adala Qatala Hoony Badala Hoon Gon’int Aman’e Qatal’a Rap’a Band Kaar Aqal’a Kessah Beka Rap’e Shakala Shakala Shakala Ka Shakala Ka Ka Shakla. Everybody tryna be me uh Imma get that blue cheese uh I’m done imma go da I’m a go dab I’m a go dab I gone imma take nap Honey, Honey…. Rap hai sara Rap Rap Rap hai sara Rap -x4. [Young Desi Rap Verses] Band wagon munday saray karday jo pailay hoya Kadday nain ganay par sunda ni moya leh dass Dud patti chaa naal rass Y’all ain’t messin with us I’m a one man army. Asli aan desi nalay baki saray farmi I alone am authentic, everyone else is generic I do it for my city I do it for my Pind, Sarson da tail, Gilli Gilli tind Jivain larda ey foji, meri camouflage dhoti Dawan thallay manji nalay, Khawan bay k roti Gallan karday nain choti Munday janday ni hunay Young Desi. Pullaya ni Culture, Anday wala burger Sohni kardi ey harkat Chaldi ey jadun mallay pay jaandi barkat circus Din poora aye na sakoon mainu, Raat sari kuriyan day phone mainu Boldi nain javin na tu bhool mainu, Call back karin tu zaroor mainu Sohni DM kardi fazool mainu Models kardiyan phone mainu, Boldi ain video ch rakh lay qabool mainu Unj e dalair nalay kuch mairay genetics, Money on my mind they call me a fanatic, Bol mairay jivain jaadu karay koi magician, Sohniyai ni tu ki janay mera ki ambition King of my city Meri chaldi permission, Bar Bar Phuchday nain maira hun, hey! Sir Sir bolday nain saray hun Tu jaanda ni mera maazi Lawan kalabazi, Raazi, Lay gaya may baazi, Rab raazi, Baki munday saray marday nain bongi, Gallan karda may taazi, Munday phuchday nain baray mairay, Tell em I’m a one man army, I’m a one man army -x2, 123, pawain burger khaa pawain lassi pee Tainu masla ki, Ey munday saray nain banday nain rapper, Taun thallay sat maran phar k may vapar Burger ketchup, putha sidda kardain nain getup, Darday nain ey saray khaanday homeopathic, Waikhdi ey mainu sohni sailiyan nu Maray koni salaiyan nu Kaindi phiray swag idda check kar Munday sunday nain ganay mairay Rokday nain gaddi nalay bolday nain Mundayan nu chaiti Young Desi aala gaana fir back kar. Shekho Young Desi aya Siddi puttay maari thaapi, Munda poora paapi, Nalay chitta kaala laynga Uttun chakkaya gandaasa Jera Nooray aakhay kharkay May pan daini naasan Lay main lahori munda shehri Phichun pind Narowal. Nazreen Shair apni kataab Listeners, the poet in his book Swag or uskay Abaoajdaad’ Swag and it’s ancestors’ Mein kehta hai keh, Umray rafta lot’ti nahin keh Mujhay anday wala burger mangaa do. Yan soday wali botal pala do, Kay yehi hay janoonay ishq ki intayhaa. Keekli kaleer di, Pag mairay veer di Dupatta mairay pai daa Fittay mu jawae daae. Sohni takdi ey Swag mera, Sadqay may javaan tera gora gora rang maiya, Pent teri ponchayan tou tang maiya Munday saray teray phichay chir gaye aa jang maiya. Lyallpur mairay yaar bhaitay. Jaanda ni pind poora Kaar kaar wajda ey Young Desi din poora Hath mairay blackberry, Tom and Jerry, paijay pairi, Jaanda ni munda saanu Swag saada zehri, Saadi chaldi a charon paasay yaar baili Bhaitay mairay court kachairi. Mainu thallay kittay baynday Tu chal chad rayn day. Young Desi. Rap hai saara Rap Rap Rap hai saara Rap -x5.
